{"tid":1539540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚9點就鳩叫到11點","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:27:31.000Z","uid":32525,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac95b9682ef5174cf6bb020a6ab230eec05c284","tid":1539540,"uid":32525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:05:50.000Z","msg":"只叫「五大訴求 缺一不可」"},{"pid":"d7470acec047920f9b4cfe11c030a16deea3f9ae","tid":1539540,"uid":148775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:09:01.000Z","msg":"[今晚10點] 窗邊大嗌：「五大訴求 缺一不可」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539413</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"abe62e584b9508331f594996a45ee224a26dddd5","tid":1539540,"uid":148775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ac95b9682ef5174cf6bb020a6ab230eec05c284","tid":1539540,"uid":32525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:05:50.000Z","msg":"只叫「五大訴求 缺一不可」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:09:14.000Z","msg":"推上熱門！"},{"pid":"50ca7ef1119526997efac437dac4224ca85d6ca0","tid":1539540,"uid":40638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:10:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc92f185a70aa01d7dd9d546b8a237769c65a136","tid":1539540,"uid":265314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:10:19.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"a6c3c9ad09d8003ace3640144a7c4803e5b11510","tid":1539540,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:10:47.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"81bad67bb82e952fde04535b1224c92e8228ca69","tid":1539540,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:12:41.000Z","msg":"【831太子恐襲】今日下午約3時，兩位親身經歷8.31太子站警察無差別襲擊事件的目擊者，於立法會議員毛孟靜陪同下召開記者會，講述事發經過及其經歷。<br />\n目擊者講出多樣警方及醫管局未有提及的消息 ，目擊者指，831傷者被送往瑪嘉烈醫院而非廣華，而早前729曾爆出有瑪嘉烈醫院醫生於Facebook稱「大大力打」，更有留言稱「唔夠架生通知聲」 、「盡情打」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民即時整合重點如下：<br />\n- 有一人失蹤<br />\n- 有機會有一人 已經死亡<br />\n   - 被警察毆打近半個鐘至嘔白泡<br />\n   - 警員見他沒有反應，方停止毆打<br />\n   - 二三十分鐘後由消防員（非救護員）送走，\u0003而該傷者完全無反應<br />\n- 警員對他們說「強姦佢地係正常」<br />\n- 有被捕人士 於警署被非禮 (摸胸)<br />\n- 於警署如廁時不能關門，同時有異性警員在場<br />\n-  有日本人被捕 ，警方拒絕讓他聯繫大使館<br />\n- 目擊者稱傷者被送去 瑪嘉烈醫院，而非廣華醫院<br />\n- 速龍落電梯時，是 用腳踩市民背部甚至頭部<br />\n<br />\n#立場新聞 直播全片：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2383919765184466/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F2383919765184466%2F&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcapmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=33d06479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2383919765184466/</a><br />\n#831太子 #太子恐襲 #毛孟靜 #立法會 <br />\n-<br />\n發聲社新聞 STP Media<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stpmedia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstpmedia&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcapmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=1b33de69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stpmedia</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.singthepress.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.singthepress.com&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcapmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=61c807ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.singthepress.com</a>"},{"pid":"30a14c594e5df591d8b992e66501ff29871de867","tid":1539540,"uid":311588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:13:11.000Z","msg":"P牌仔push"},{"pid":"3d7c975c3475634a2aaddc528414ae7b189da6fc","tid":1539540,"uid":32525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:25:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"510b1a084c4882232d3891d7adcf626afdd222fa","tid":1539540,"uid":278116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:27:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35ce38f7f7eff864a11df6fab8bee67de528d27b","tid":1539540,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:27:31.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>缺一不可</strong></span></span><br />\n咪撚改口號<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">送中仲未正式撤回 依家只係動議</span></span><br />\n<blockquote>林鄭又想過鳩我地一棟啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539720</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母仲要等復會 再提出撤回議案<br />\n而立法會復會係10月9或10月16日<br />\n重點就係呢到：10月1國慶<br />\n今日無啦啦出黎廢up<br />\n擺明就係想側側搏 係10月1日前盡快平息件事<br />\n等佢可以平平安安渡過鄰國國慶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求下你地睇埋呢篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家點睇脫共？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536794\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536794</a>"}]}